            <div type="section" xml:id="Legislation">
                <head>Legislation</head>
                <p>There is no specific legislation governing the access to diplomatic archives.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="section" xml:id="Location">
                <head>Location</head>
                <p>National Archives: Ministry of Youth, Culture and Sports, B.P. 1095, Rohero II -
                    avenue Kunkiko, Bujumbura.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="section" xml:id="Procedures">
                <head> Procedures</head>
                <p>Researchers should write to the National Archives and to the nearest Burundi
                    Embassy to inquire about access to diplomatic records. </p>
            </div>
            <div type="section" xml:id="Website">
                <head>Website</head>
